item.description: I have changed the time on this Meetup as the days are getting shorter. Don't worry if you'll be late, just come whenever you can. This is a great park for fetch, running and just playing. We just like to get in that evening of stressfree, no pavement play. As always bring bug spray, water, toys and relaxing outlook. It's a nice evening for humans as well as our four legged friends. See you at the park. "WOOF"
item.how_to_find_us: Jack, Bella and I will be out in the fields.
